    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/34f1c860b8d020d1f09ae6dd1712e42e.avif?t=1749137133\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras_big/34f1c860b8d020d1f09ae6dd1712e42e.avif?t=1749137133 width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An upcoming <strong>story-driven fantasy RPG</strong>, <i>Tales from Frah’Akin</i> blends the charm of classic RPGs with modern mechanics and <strong>cinematic cutscenes</strong>, all crafted by a solo Polish developer, <strong>Aeghite</strong>, using RPG Maker MZ. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/2016eb80d748033c8301b510352702b8.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/5eefaeb295aa471ed91e9b0b907fb993.poster.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/5eefaeb295aa471ed91e9b0b907fb993.webm?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/5eefaeb295aa471ed91e9b0b907fb993.mp4?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of <strong>Ennea</strong>, princess of the <strong>Forest Elves</strong>, and embark on a journey across the magical land of <strong>Frah’Akin</strong>. Uncover the secrets of a looming threat that endangers the elven realm, forge bonds with unique companions, and reveal hidden truths about the past, present, and future. <strong>Your choices will shape the world around you — and the people in it!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In special scenes, you’ll even get to <strong>play as other main characters</strong>, diving into their personal memories and perspectives. Romance, friendship, conflict — every relationship holds the power to change the course of your story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/9d5ef97f6ec67ae272b7d4891d4792a4.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/97f0636a6174ca03dce73558743940c0.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/a47bf823b4e1ed90e153b959b6df8457.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/379625ad592ad718467abd8a7c92e077.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/ca43ee618ae5e86e0d0f1820282a0707.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/fde65470b36567bc6daedf6c0973f408.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/2bbcacc15cfda5c81c193987701841b9.poster.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/2bbcacc15cfda5c81c193987701841b9.webm?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/2bbcacc15cfda5c81c193987701841b9.mp4?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No random encounters! See your enemies before battle and choose when to engage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combo skills</strong> – Unleash powerful team-based attacks to defeat enemies efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto-battle system</strong> – Speed up battles while farming and leveling up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/b101694998c73da66cfc909b48182063.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/31c2a2e870a609aa2ea89f86ac4f3901.poster.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/31c2a2e870a609aa2ea89f86ac4f3901.webm?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/31c2a2e870a609aa2ea89f86ac4f3901.mp4?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive worldbuilding</strong> – Interact with NPCs, complete side quests, and uncover rich lore and character backstories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration &amp; rewards</strong> – Find hidden treasures, uncover secrets, and enjoy various <strong>mini-games</strong> including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎣 Fishing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎼 Playing instruments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💃 Dancing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 Training animals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛏️ Mining</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crafting &amp; customization</strong> – Gather ingredients, craft potions, and forge your own weapons and armor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/72283036e5ac2944fe1d66d4c7b86a95.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/e4bfb1ad3f396ffe91c797437425c374.poster.avif?t=1749137133\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/e4bfb1ad3f396ffe91c797437425c374.webm?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063950/extras/e4bfb1ad3f396ffe91c797437425c374.mp4?t=1749137133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>13 playable characters</strong>, each with a unique skill set, personal questline, and backstory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Two outfit sets per character.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>A variety of interactive mini-games.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>No random encounters!</strong> Choose your battles strategically.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Custom hand-drawn art</strong>, including scene-based CGs and expressive character busts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Original soundtrack</strong> with a captivating, fairy-tale-like main theme.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Character interactions &amp; romances.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>English &amp; Polish language support.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌿 <strong>Fully voice-acted demo.</strong></p>",
